*gaim-0.59.8-r1 (13 Jan 2003)

  13 Jan 2003; Nick Hadaway <raker@gentoo.org> gaim-0.59.8-r1.ebuild,
  files/digest-gaim-0.59.8-r1 :
  Added ssl support via the encrypt plugin provided at
  gaim-encryption.sourcforge.net.  Also removed the gtk2 logic as
  all the gtk2 code has been ripped out as of this version.  Use
  gaim-cvs for a gtk2 enabled build of gaim.

